high_descs: Walk ahead, and then veer right to the sink.
Pick up the knife to the left of the sink.
Wash the knife in the sink.
Open the drawer in the corner, the one on the right side counter. Place the knife in it.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean knife in a drawer.

high_descs: Walk forward, then hang a left and walk over to the sink.
Pick up the butter knife off of the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Put the butter knife in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean butter knife.
Turn left to face the counter.
Open the last drawer on your right and put the clean butter knife inside, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean butter knife in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the sink.
Pick up the knife on the left side of the sink.
Go to the right side of the sink.
Rinse off the knife in the sink and pick it back up.
Turn left toward the bread on the counter.
Put the knife in the drawer below the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed off knife in the drawer.
